; Forecast should include current month's budget (GitHub issue #1576)
;
; When using --forecast, the period that contains the current date
; should be included in the output, not skipped.

~ Monthly
    Expenses:Rent             $1000.00
    Assets:Checking

test reg --forecast-while "date < [2011/06/01]" --now "2011/03/15" --columns 80
11-Mar-01 Forecast transaction  Expenses:Rent              $1000.00     $1000.00
11-Mar-01 Forecast transaction  Assets:Checking           $-1000.00            0
11-Apr-01 Forecast transaction  Expenses:Rent              $1000.00     $1000.00
11-Apr-01 Forecast transaction  Assets:Checking           $-1000.00            0
11-May-01 Forecast transaction  Expenses:Rent              $1000.00     $1000.00
11-May-01 Forecast transaction  Assets:Checking           $-1000.00            0
end test
